new_skill_specs.name: extract_accuracy_scores_from_chart
new_skill_specs.purpose: Extract accuracy scores for different models from a chart at a specified pretrain loss value.
new_skill_specs.outputs: A dictionary with model names as keys and their corresponding accuracy scores as values.
edge_cases: Chart is unclear or values are not precisely at the specified pretrain loss value.

new_skill_specs.name: determine_highest_accuracy_model
new_skill_specs.purpose: Determine which model has the highest accuracy score from a given set of scores.
new_skill_specs.outputs: The name of the model with the highest accuracy score.
edge_cases: Multiple models have the same highest accuracy score.
